# API Types

- Read `packages/api-types/README.md` and `SPEC.md` before changing shared contracts.
- Keep this package free of business logic, fetch wrappers, route ownership, and UI view models.
- Mirror public server contracts from `services/backend` and `services/ai-backend`; do not model `/internal/v1/*` here.
- Treat enum removals, required-field additions, and response field removals as breaking changes that need a migration note.
- Run `npm run typecheck --workspace @0x-copilot/api-types` and frontend typecheck when practical.
